```plantuml
@startuml Enterprise-CMCS_macpro-appian-connector

actor Developer
participant "GitHub Repository" as Repo
participant "GitHub Actions" as GH
participant "ECS Task" as ECS
participant "Appian" as Appian
participant "Kafka Connector" as Connector
participant "BigMAC" as BigMAC
participant "SNS" as SNS
participant "CloudWatch" as CW

Developer -> Repo: Commit Changes
Repo -> GH: Trigger CI/CD Workflow
GH -> ECS: Deploy Connector
ECS -> Appian: Request Data Changes
Appian -> Connector: Provide Data Changes
Connector -> BigMAC: Stream Data
Connector -> CW: Log Performance Metrics
Connector -> SNS: Notify on Application Health
SNS -> Developer: Alert Notifications

@enduml
```